data.description: This three bedroom, two bath home sits in a well established neighborhood in the Waiakea area.  Casement windows add to the design, also catching lots of breeze coming from different directions to flow through the home. Three closets throughout the hallway, as well as a walk in closet in the master bedroom allow for lots of storage space for your things inside your home.  Outside of the dining room is a covered lanai for easy entertaining or relaxing.  The attached garage has an automatic door, and lots of mounted cabinets for additional storage.  BONUS: there is an additional garage, detached from the home, with an automatic door as well!  Don't have the need for two garages?  Use it as a workspace, entertaining area, or anything you can imagine!  This home is great as it is, or put a little of your own touch into it...  The possibilities are endless!
